   367→    name: "wiki_next_task",
   368→    description: "Get the next task for the Not-Wikipedia autonomous agent. Uses cryptographically secure randomness combined with ecosystem state to select: task type, researcher, article type, category, and infobox color. For new content creation, fetches a human-written text passage (quote or literary excerpt) as creative inspiration. Returns a complete task specification.",
